node.text:
Here’s how to win a free trip to @breakaway music festival: 

1. Follow all 4 accounts we’re following on Instagram
2. Subscribe to our YouTube channel by swiping up on our story

After that, you could be commencing suckdown on stage at @breakawayohio with us and @djpressplay on September 4th.

We’re picking two followers (plus 1 friend each) to fly out for a weekend of sweet suds and tasty licks.

All ya gotta do are those two steps above. Pretty standard stuff, really.

Good luck and Godspeed 🤝
